							        <figure class="media-figure img-inset-thumb" data-click-tracking="genericClickCbsNews" data-omniture-track-data='{"clickProperty": "60 Minutes Asset|Content Video Player|Extra|Recent Asset-11|Thumbnail"}'><span class="img "><img src="https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2016/01/30/c6b0f5e9-c551-43af-87c9-28df20e4bf3e/thumbnail/170x95/5b9021ecec916e2657258be35897f349/previewgreenland10.jpg#" alt=" " height="95" width="170" class=" lazyload" data-srcset="https://cbsnews3.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2016/01/30/c6b0f5e9-c551-43af-87c9-28df20e4bf3e/thumbnail/170x95/5b9021ecec916e2657258be35897f349/previewgreenland10.jpg 1x, https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2016/01/30/c6b0f5e9-c551-43af-87c9-28df20e4bf3e/thumbnail/340x190/2969143edf2680b11443d8f20fff9c5f/previewgreenland10.jpg 2x" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI="></span>
									</figure></a>
								<div class="media-body">
